    "finalText": "Draft preview:\n\nSubject: Submittal Turnaround\n\nAcme Roofing,\n\nYour submittal turnaround is now impacting our ability to keep the job moving.\n\nWe need your team to return outstanding submittals promptly and keep pace with the required review cycle going forward. At this point, the delay is holding up downstream work and creating avoidable schedule pressure.\n\nSend back a clear status on all open submittals, including what is complete, what is still pending, and the date we will have the remaining items in hand. If there is an issue preventing turnaround, raise it now so we can address it immediately.\n\nWe need this corrected right away.\n\nThanks,  \nBrandon\n\nIf you want, I can turn this into an Outlook draft and make it a little sharper or more diplomatic depending on the relationship."
